      "content": "That feeling of losing your \"soul\" and feeling like a hollow machine is incredibly painful, but it is a symptom of depression rather than an actual erasure of your humanity. The \"you\" that is still there is capable of healing and reconnecting with purpose, even if it feels completely absent right now. Please consider reaching out to a crisis line or a therapist who can help you navigate this loss and rebuild your sense of self.",
      "source": "target",
